content.description:
Lie back to a small roof then up a shallow right facing corner to the top.  Just around the corner fifty feet from LedZep Arette towards the highway

Tangerine,  5.7
content.location:
lost cabin crag

descent is 4th class to the south

also there is a 10 c top rope finger crack slab facing the highway with an old cable at top for an anchor.

content.location:
this is just 200 feet from the highway near the site of the old forest service cabin which was torn down- the lost cabin crag sets in trees just off the road!  see attached maps
